Definition: pantropical tree of usually seacoasts sometimes cultivated as an ornamental for its rounded heart-shaped leaves and showy yellow and purple flowers
Example: yields valuable pink to dark red close-grained wood and oil from its seeds
Synonyms: bendy_tree, seaside_mahoe, Thespesia_populnea, tulipwood_tree, genus_Thespesia, m, pantropical, tree, of, usually, seacoasts, sometimes, cultivated, as, an, ornamental, for, its, rounded, heart-shaped, leaves, and, showy, yellow, purple, flowers, yields, valuable, pink, to, dark, red, close-grained, wood, oil, from, seeds
Category: noun.plant
